Photos, snapshots of a day that the head of the executive defines "historical". >&nbsp;Why&nbsp;seppur focuses on the funeral of Pope Francis ("To God", the greeting of Meloni who posted on social media, accompanied by an image with the Pontiff) is served to take steps forward in the conflict between Kiev and Moscow. >
Meloni has worked under-trace to bring Trump and Zelensky together and above all to make sure that between the European institutions and the United States there was a first contact, now it will be just to fix the date of an official meeting to avoid another war, the commercial one. But it's about the war in Ukraine that Trump wanted to accelerate. It has not set any deadline, but in American plans there would be the will to start the ceasefire on May 1 (with the announcement of the breakthrough a few days earlier). To arrive at the ceasefire unconditional - both Macron and Meloni have underlined how Zelensky agrees on the objective - will make a further pressing towards Russia. "It's up to President Putin to prove he really wants peace," said the Elisean tenant.
"Now we are expected that Russia also demonstrates its willingness to pursue peace," the Italian premier relaunched, while Trump expressed the fear that the 'zar' does not want to stop the war and "that is just making fun of me", which is why he assumes that it is necessary to face the situation "differently", through new sanctions.
"See Donald Trump and Volodymyr Zelensky who speak of peace at the funeral of the 'Papa della pace' &nbsp; has a huge meaning", said to Republic the President of the Council, who did not participate in the <a href="https://www.agi.it/estero/news/2025-04-26/zelensky-trump-starmer-macron-san-pietro-311022 &nbsp;>
&nbsp;
